entries.abort: You can't just leave me here! We have a mission to finish!
entries.arrival_phase_1: The freightor should be here any time now.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Pilot! There it is! Go get it!
entries.attack_notify: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Scanning... Warning! Hostile vessels incoming with weapon systems armed!>
entries.attack_stopped: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Scanning... No hostile enemies detected in the vacinity.>
entries.capture_phase_1: What do you think you are doing? These are supplies for Nova Industries! Cease and desist immediately!
entries.capture_phase_2: Your too late! I have already reported your actions, reinfor.....  Ugh... Capture complete sir. Lets get these supplies back before the reinforcments arrive.
entries.capture_started: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Capture process beginning in 3.. 2.. 1..>
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Enemy escort has been destroyed!>
entries.failed_destroy: You let them destory the supplies! What were you thinking!?
entries.failed_escape: You let them get away! You had better hope they dont know you work for Orion. Get back here on the double!
entries.panic_1: I can't do anything in this worthless wreck. Get them off me!
entries.panic_2: Pilot! I'm counting on you to take care of these villains!
entries.quest_disable_d: Disable the freightor so it can be boarded and taken over.
entries.quest_escort_d: The hijacked ship needs an escort back, so Nova cannot get it back.
entries.quest_location_d: Sector of Ord Mantell space currently housing Nova Orion Industries
entries.quest_recover_d: The disabled ship needs to be captured, so it can be redirected back to base.
entries.recovery_success: Pilot, our mission was a success! Nova will never recieve those supplies he needs!
entries.target_disabled: The supply ship has been disabled. Good work. Now, our spy onboard will take over.
entries.taunt_1: You'll never take these supplies you Orion Scum!
entries.thanks_2: Glad to have you here, pilot.
entries.title: Supplies Redistributed
entries.title_d: Nova thinks to resupply his fighters, but we have worked too hard for that to happen. We are going to take those supplies back for ourselves.
